Name: childhood ovarian endodermal sinus tumor
Definition: An ovarian endodermal sinus tumor that presents in childhood.

Name: glandular pattern ovarian yolk sac tumor
Definition: An ovarian endodermal sinus tumor that is characterized by a glandular pattern on histology.
Synonym: Occult squamous cell carcinoma of the lung

Name: hepatoid pattern ovarian yolk sac tumor
Definition: An ovarian endodermal sinus tumor that is characterized by a hepatoid pattern on histology
Synonym: Occult squamous cell carcinoma of the lung

Name: polyvesicular vitelline pattern ovarian yolk sac tumor
Definition: An ovarian endodermal sinus tumor that is characterized by a polyvesicular vitelline pattern
